name: Therapy App UI + Prototype
description:
A concept application designed for a university course project. The application adapts to the user's needs and provides the appropriate content. A personal journal is also available recording moods, sleep cycles, and more. A therapist can also be hired and contacted for therapy sessions.

There are two demos available, one of which was used for the report and one which was used for a live demo during the presentation. Two watch screens are also present, the mockups of which were used for visuals only.
